title: Bye Bye Baby (Taylor's Version) (From The Vault)
description:
It's the last track on the Fearless (Taylor's Version) (From The Vault), and it's the perfect ender to this era. What's all the juicy info behind this song? Amy, Lacey, Ana and Nick break it all down!
What did we miss? What are you excited to hear? There are so many ways to reach us!
